The Bund Business Park, 580-600 Lorimer Street

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to exclusively offer the last remaining units at 'The Bund' Business Park, located at 580-600 Lorimer Street, Port Melbourne, now available for lease.

This unrivalled development offers tenants new office/warehouses ranging from 500sqm - 3,000sqm* along with waterfront views of the Port of Melbourne. The Bund is now complete and ready for occupation.

Property features include:
+ Multi-level office/showroom and warehouse buildings from 500sqm - 3,000sqm*
+ Large internal estate road and exclusive carpark and loading areas
+ Ability to combine buildings to create larger facilities
+ High clearance / clear span warehousing
+ Waterfront views
+ Modern amenities
+ Container height roller doors
+ 3 phase power
+ Open plan office space
+ Long term leases available within Port Melbourne's developing employment precinct
+ Immediate access to Citylink, Monash Freeway & West Gate Freeway
+ 3km* from the CBD, 1km* from the Port and 17km* from the Melbourne International Airport

For further details on this property or your Port Melbourne commercial property needs, please contact the exclusive marketing agents from CBRE.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LAST REMAINING UNITS AVAILABLE: HI-TECH INDUSTRIAL ESTATE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to present, For Lease, this outstanding first floor office located at 5 Westside Avenue, Port Melbourne.

Fitted out to the highest of standards, this secure office comes with ample parking, large boardroom, kitchenette and additional storage space. 

Located off both Lorimer Street and Salmon Street, the property is ideally suited to operate your business, with good amenity within walking distance. Flexible lease terms are available.

Property Highlights:
+ High quality office area: 892 sqm*
+ Boardroom & meeting rooms
+ On-site car parks
+ Access to the CBD and freeways
+ Good amenity within walking distance for both staff and clients

All reasonable offers considered.

*approx.
